{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-remark-twemoji-shortcut","description":"Add twitter emoji to gatsby markdown.","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","gatsby-remark","emoji","markdown"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"tri613","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/060e66bb7ead7990fdb9d0eca6d37a7c"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/tri613/gatsby-remark-twemoji-shortcut"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-remark-twemoji-shortcut\"><a href=\"#gatsby-remark-twemoji-shortcut\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-remark-twemoji-shortcut</h1>\n<p>A <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/tree/master/packages/gatsby-transformer-remark\">gatsby-transformer-remark</a> plugin to add twitter emoji with shortcuts! :sparkles:</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<h3 id=\"install-package\"><a href=\"#install-package\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install package</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add gatsby-remark-twemoji-shortcut</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>or </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install gatsby-remark-twemoji-shortcut</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h3 id=\"add-to-your-code-classlanguage-textgatsby-configjscode\"><a href=\"#add-to-your-code-classlanguage-textgatsby-configjscode\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Add to your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n          <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-prismjs`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// some other remark plugins</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-twemoji-shortcut`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              classname<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'some_classname another_classname'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// add additional classname(s) to the emoji</span>\n              style<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> \n                <span class=\"token comment\">// add additional inline-styling to the emoji</span>\n                background<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gold'</span>\n              <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ...other plugins</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The default classname is <code class=\"language-text\">emoji</code> (from twemoji) and will not be removed when additional classname is set.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The default inline styles are as <a href=\"https://github.com/twitter/twemoji#inline-styles\">twemoji suggested</a>:</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\">\n      <pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">img.emoji</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 .05em 0 .1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token property\">vertical-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -0.1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>The styles will be merged with default and additional (option) styles.\nIf you pass in a css property which exists in the default, the default style would be overwritten by the additional style.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<p>Just write emoji shortcuts in your markdown and it will be transformed into twitter emojis!</p>\n<p>A markdown post like this:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\">\n      <pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">---\ndatetime: &quot;2018-06-13 15:33:38&quot;\ntitle: &quot;Twitter Emojis!&quot;\ntags: [&quot;emoji&quot;, &quot;twitter&quot;, &quot;plugin&quot;]\n---\n\nAdd twitter emojis with no sweat. :sunglasses::heart::tada::sparkles:</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Get turns into this:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QBnHp2s.png\"></p>\n<p>Thatâ€™s it! :tada:</p>\n<p>:point_right: This plugin also converts plain emojis (unicode) into twitter emojis!</p>\n<h2 id=\"special-thanks\"><a href=\"#special-thanks\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Special Thanks</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The shortcut emoji mapping is pulled from <a href=\"https://github.com/github/gemoji\">gemoji</a>, huge thanks for this awesome list.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>This repo is inspired by another great gatsby remark emoji plugin: <a href=\"https://github.com/matchilling/gatsby-remark-emojis\">https://github.com/matchilling/gatsby-remark-emojis</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":2}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-remark-twemoji-shortcut/","id":"3035fb49-371c-5c92-bbeb-787e1725d60f"}}